name: deadlines #01
description:
The human being's ability to make so many incredible tones of color with such imperceptible transitions.

Handmade oil painting on canvas (by an unknown-almost-artist who died in 2017) turns into over 10,000 vectors and 6,000 colors. The same painting, the same colors and tones in random vectors.

Simple but amazing!

Stay tuned! Soon new tones, new transformations and new and exclusive oil paintings on canvas.
